responseText: Those goblins live in filth, they basically leave a trail of garbage everywhere they go. Then I get put on trashfire duty and have to burn it all up. It never ends. Listen, if you find yourself schlepping around a bunch of twigs and stuff, just give it to one of us. We'll take care of it.
name: SQ_NPC_RVR_Batyard_Tenders_1_Response
